title: Cancer: Vegans are Lying to You (vs. Mic the Vegan)
description:
The earlier video mentioned (vs. Mic the Vegan) is: "Mic the Vegan IS WRONG: Brain Damage from THC." https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EUbyVBi8Ams
The source of the 15% statistic is: *"Vegetarian, vegan diets and multiple health outcomes: A systematic review with meta-analysis of observational studies."*
[Authors:] Dinu M, Abbate R, Gensini GF, Casini A, Sofi F.
Crit Rev Food Sci Nutr. 2017 Nov 22;57(17):3640-3649. doi: 10.1080/10408398.2016.1138447.
PMID: 26853923 DOI: 10.1080/10408398.2016.1138447
